{
  "stem": "3952.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In fact, I don't know if they worked at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were-- they were confined to their-- to their houses where they were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So at first, we saw the Italians walking through Sighet, and Germans we saw very little of, very few, very few.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Here and there you would see a German, but not really, not the army, not the German army we didn't see.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We knew what they are doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We knew what they are doing to-- to Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We knew that the Czechs ran away from them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We-- we have seen Jewish people who ran away who came-- very few, about two or three of them-- who came to our synagogues and told us about the atrocities of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were telling that they are simply digging huge pits and-- and-- and having the Jews take their clothes off.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jews had to dig their own graves, their own pits, and they would just shoot them in the line, like we know already later.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw them on films.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at that time, they were telling us, and we said, no, they are crazy, because those people acted a little nervous.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And naturally, now we understand why, because if you go through something like that, you-- you cannot stay normal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "None of us survivors is 100% normal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have our fears to live with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have a lot of things to-- to remember, and-- and to relive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Each time we talk about it, we have dreams at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm probably going to dream about this tonight also, because I dreamt when I spoke in front of those children that I mentioned before to you, in private, off camera.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I spoke-- I spoke in front of a high school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were like 120 boys from 15 to 18.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
